node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 06, 2021 tagging @tylerbossetti. May be an image of text that says 'Tyler Bossetti @tylerbossetti 3 mentality shifts that helped me take control of my life...'.

node.text:
Like most other people, @tylerbossetti didn't have a perfect upbringing but he didn't let that get in his way.

He got out of his toxic environment by becoming a door-to-door salesman and eventually transitioning into the mortgage industry, where he would learn the ins and outs of real estate.

He then used that knowledge to build a real estate fund that helps others invest in great real estate deals without doing any of the work.

If he can do it, anyone can.

Go follow him, he's putting out some great content @tylerbossetti 🔥

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 06, 2021 tagging @richardyuzee. May be an image of text that says 'Richard Yu @richardyuzee 5 biggest mistakes made as a beginner entrepreneur...'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 06, 2021 tagging @richardyuzee. May be an image of text that says 'Richard Yu @richardyuzee 1. Lack of consistency. Your success will NEVER exceed your habits, and I had inconsistent sleep times, diet, and work times.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 06, 2021 tagging @richardyuzee. May be an image of text that says 'Richard Yu @richardyuzee 2. Porn Addiction. Super vulnerable here, but struggled with this for YEARS (99% of guys do), and never took ownership over this.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 06, 2021 tagging @richardyuzee. May be an image of text that says 'Richard Yu @richardyuzee 3. Shiny Object Syndrome. I failed 4 businesses before I succeeded with my 5th because was constantly chasing new business after new business.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 06, 2021 tagging @richardyuzee. May be an image of text that says 'Richard Yu @richardyuzee 4.1 cared more about money than impact. just wanted to hustle and make money and lost sight of the whole point of entrepreneurship. To ADD VALUE to the lives of others, and as a result of that, you make money.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 06, 2021 tagging @richardyuzee. May be an image of text that says 'Richard Yu @richardyuzee 5. Lack of congruency with my faith in God. I went to church, read the Bible, and "looked" like I was a person of faith, but my heart and actions didn't align with it. The second started to do things for God, my business skyrocketed.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 06, 2021 tagging @richardyuzee. May be an image of text that says 'Richard Yu @richardyuzee So those are the biggest mistakes I regret making when I first started in business. If you're serious about your success, avoid these at all cost.'.
